<span class="headers">*Costs: Smithed Items</span>
<p>
<p align="left">Prices listed are using best charisma and faction, in 
platinum pieces in decimal form with no currency label: 9.524 would mean 9pp 5gp 2sp 4cp.</p>
<p align="left">Please note that the followng items are not yet listed 
on this page due to incomplete data. They will be added as info is gathered.:
<ul>
<li>	small piece of HQ ore</li>
<li>	block of HQ ore</li>
<li>	sheet of velium</li>
<li>	forging hammer</li>
<li>	brick of black acrylia</li>
<li>	bloodling carapace</li>
</ul>
</p>
<p align="center"><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/sources/source_trade_page.php?st=Smithing&menustr=110110000000">Smithing 
supplies</a> &#8212; <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/recipes/recipe_page.php?article=57&rsa=Smithing&sb=item&sub=other&menustr=080100000000">Smithing 
recipes</a><br>
On this page: </b>Ingredient Costs</b> Smithing Prices: <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g194&menustr=070090000000#basics">Basic Metalworking</a> &#8212; <a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/articles/article_page.php?article=g194&menustr=070090000000#tools">Smithed Tools</a><br>
